creator: ra.mc@mail.telepac.pt
text:
Add processing of external links of the form "F.pdf#ND" 
and "F.pdf#nameddest=ND".

The syntax currently supported ("F.pdf#dest=ND") is not supported by Acrobat 
(http://www.adobe.com/support/techdocs/a17e.htm), so it may not work if you 
use it when rendering other formats besides PDF.

creator: pascal.sancho@takoma.fr
text:
this feature was readded in FOP 0.94.
FOP Web site says that is not yet readded... (see
http://xmlgraphics.apache.org/fop/0.94/extensions.html#named-destinations).
Therefore this bug should be left opened until Website is corrected.
